flowchart TD
    A[Input situation or dialogue] --> B[Retrieval / Source context]
    B --> C[Telemetry read: RC, E, TC, CS, V]
    C --> D[COM parse: domain, node, status]
    D --> E[Operator admissibility]
    E --> F{Budget and telemetry pass?}
    F -- yes --> G[Candidate response / COM-Log]
    F -- no --> H[Risk throttle: downgrade, hold, clarify, recheck]
    G --> I[Validator]
    H --> I
    I --> J{Release allowed?}
    J -- yes --> K[Output]
    J -- no --> L[Rewrite / regenerate / fallback]
    K --> M[Self-audit / memory telemetry]
    L --> M
    M --> C
